hadiths[172]{hadithnumber,text}:
349,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere ghar ki chhat khol di gaee, us waqt main Makka mein tha. phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) utrey aur unhon-ne mera Sina chaak kya. phir usey zamzam ke pani se dhoya. phir aik soney ka tasht laey jo hikmat aur eman se bharaa hua tha. usko mere seeney mein rakh diya, phir seeney ko jod diya, phir mera hath pakda aur mujhey aasman ki taraf lekar chaley. jab main pahley aasman par pahuncha to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aasman ke darogha se kaha kholo. usne poochha, aap kon hain? jawab diya ke Jibraeel, phir unhon-ne puchha kya aap ke sath koi aur bhi hai? jawab diya, haan mere sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. unhon-ne puchha ke kya unke bulaney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha? kaha, ji haan! phir jab unhon-ne darwaza khola to ham pahley aasman par chadh gaey, wahan ham ne aik shakhs ko baithey huey dekha. unke dahini taraf kuchh logon ke jhund they aur kuchh jhund baain taraf they. jab wo apni dahini taraf dekhtey to muskuraa detey aur jab baain taraf nazar kartey to rotey. unhon-ne mujhey dekh kar farmaya, aao achchhey aaey ho. Saleh Nabi aur Saleh betey ! maine Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) se puchha ye kon hain? unhon-ne kaha ke ye Adam (Alaihissalam) hain aur unke daaein-baaein jo jhund hain ye unke beton ki roohein hain. jo jhund daain taraf hain wo jannati hain aur baain taraf ke jhund dozakhi roohein hain. isliye jab wo apne daain taraf dekhtey hain to khushi se muskuratey hain aur jab baain taraf dekhtey hain to (ranj se) rotey hain. phir Jibraeel mujhey lekar doosrey aasman tak pahunchey aur uske darogha se kaha ke kholo. us aasman ke darogha ne bhi pahley ki tarah puchha phir khol diya. Anas ne kaha ke Abu-Zar ne zikr kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aasman par Aadam, Idrees, Moosaa, Esa aur Ibrahim ko maujood paya aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne har aik ka thikana nahi bayan kya. albatta itna bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Adam ko pahley aasman par paya aur Ibrahim ko chhatey aasman par. Anas ne bayan kya ke jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Idrees (Alaihissalam) par guzrey. to unhon-ne farmaya ke aao achchhey aaey ho Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhaaii. maine puchha ye kon hain? jawab diya ke ye Idrees (Alaihissalam) hain. phir Musa (Alaihissalam) tak pahuncha to unhon-ne farmaya aao achchhey aaey ho Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhaaii. maine puchha ye kon hain? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) hain. phir mein Esa (Alaihissalam) tak pahuncha, unhon-ne kaha aao achchhey aaey ho Saleh Nabi aur Saleh bhaaii. maine puchha ye kon hain? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Esa (Alaihissalam) hain. phir main Ibrahim tak pahuncha. unhon-ne farmaya aao achchhey aaey ho Saleh Nabi aur Saleh betey. maine puchha ye kon hain? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Ibrahim hain. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujhey abu-Bakar-bin-Hazam ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin-Abbas aur Abu-Hiba Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, phir mujhey Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) lekar chadhey, ab main us buland maqam tak pahunch gaya jahan maine qalam ki awaz suni (jo likhney waley farishton ki qalmon ki awaz thi) ibne-Hazam ne (apne Shekh se) aur Anas-bin-Malik ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se naql kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, to Allah Taala ne meri ummat par pachaas waqt ki namazein farz kiin. main ye hukm lekar wapas lautaa. jab Musa (Alaihissalam) tak pahuncha to unhon-ne puchha ke aap ki ummat par Allah ne kya farz kya hai? maine kaha ke pachaas waqt ki namazein farz ki hain. unhon-ne farmaya aap wapas apne rab ki bargah mein jaaiye. kyonke aap ki ummat itni namazon ko ada karne ki taqat nahi rakhti hai. main wapas rabbul-izzat ki bargah mein gaya to Allah ne usmein se aik hissey kam kar diya, phir Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke aik hissey kam kar diya gaya hai, unhon-ne kaha ke dobara jaaiye kyonke aap ki ummat mein iske bardasht ki bhi taqat nahi hai. phir mein rabbul-izzat kii baargaah mein hazir hua. phir aik hissey kam hua. jab Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas pahuncha to unhon-ne farmaya ke apne rab ki bargah mein phir jaaiye, kyonke aap ki ummat usko bhi bardasht na kar sakey gii, phir main baar-baar aaya gaya to Allah Taala ne farmaya ke ye namazein (amal mein) panch hain aur) sawab mein) pachaas (ke barabar ( hain. meri baat badli nahi jati. ab main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhon-ne phir kaha ke apne rab ke paas jaaiye. lekin maine kaha mujhey ab apne rab se sharm aati hai. phir Jibraeel mujhey sidratul-Muntahaa tak le gaey jisey kai tarah ke rangon ne dhaank rakha tha. jinke mutaalliq mujhey malum nahi hua ke wo kya hain. iske baad mujhey jannat mein ley jaya gaya, maine dekha ke usmein motiyon ke haar hain aur uski mitti mashk ki hai."
350,Allah Taala ne pahley Namaz mein 2-2 rakaat farz ki thi. safar mein bhi aur iqamat ki haalat mein bhii. phir safar ki Namaz to apni aslii haalat par baqi rakhi gaee aur haalat iqamat ki namazon mein zyadti kar di gaee.
351,"hamein hukm hua ke ham dono eidon ke din haaiza aur parda nasheen aurton ko bhi bahar ley jaaein. taake wo musalmanon ke ijtimaa aur unki duaon mein Sharik ho sakein . albatta haaiza aurton ko Namaz padhney ki jagah se door rakhein. aik aurat ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! ham mein kuchh auratein aisi bhi hoti hain jinke paas ( parda karne ke liye) chadar nahi hoti . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski sathi aurat apni chadar ka aik hissey usey udha de. aur Abdullah-bin -Rijaa ne kaha ham se Imran qattaan ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Muhammad-bin Sirin ne, kaha ham se umme-Atiya ne, maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aur yahi hadis bayan ki."
352,Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne tehband baandh kar Namaz padhi. jisey unhon-ne sar tak baandh rakha tha aur aap ke kapdey khoontii par tangey huey they. aik kehney waley ne kaha ke aap aik tehband mein Namaz padhtey hain? aap ne jawab diya ke maine aisa isliye kya ke tujh jaisa koi ahmaq mujhey dekhey. bhala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein 2 kapdey bhi kis ke paas they?
353,maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha aur unhon-ne batlaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi aik hi kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha tha.
354,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kapdey mein Namaz padhi aur aap ne kapdey ke donon kinaron ko mukhalif taraf ke kaandhey par daal liya.
355,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Umme-Salma ke ghar mein aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha, kapdey ke donon kinaron ko aap ne donon kandhon par daal rakha tha."
356,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey huey dekha, aap usey lapetey huey they aur uske donon kinaron ko donon kandhon par daley huey they."
357,"mein fateh Makka ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. maine dekha ke aap ghusl kar rahe hain aur aap ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) parda kiye huey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kon hai? maine bataya ke Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achi aai ho, Umme-Hani . phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nahaaney se farigh ho gaey to uthey aur aath (8) rakaat Namaz padhi, aik hi kapdey mein lipat kar. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh chukey to maine kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! meri maa ke betey ( Ali-bin abi-Talib (ka dawa hai ke wo aik shakhs ko zaroor qatl karega . halanke maine usey panah de rakhi hai. ye ( mere khawind ( Hubaira ka falan betaa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umme-Hani jisey tum ne panah de di, ham ne bhi usey panah di. Umme-Hani ne kaha ke ye namaaze-chaasht thi."
358,aik poochhney waley ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik kapdey mein Namaz padhney ke mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (kuchh bura nahin) bhala kya tum sab mein har shakhs ke paas 2 kapdey hain?
359,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi shakhs ko bhi aik kapdey mein Namaz is tarah na padhni chahiye ke iske kandhon par kuchh na ho.
360,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farmatey they. main uski gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine ye irshad farmatey suna tha ke jo shakhs aik kapdey mein Namaz padhey usey kapdey ke donon kinaron ko iske mukhalif samt ke kandhey par daal lena chahiye"
361,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar ( jang bawaat ( mein gaya. aik raat mein kisi zarurat ki wjah se aap ke paas aaya. maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein mashghool hain, us waqt mere badan par sirf aik hi kapda tha. isliye maine usey lapet liya aur aap ke bazu mein ho kar mein bhi Namaz mein Sharik ho gaya. jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to malum farmaya Jaabir us raat ke waqt kaisey aaey? maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni zarurat ke mutaalliq kaha, mein jab farigh ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke ye tum ne kya lapet rakha tha jisey maine dekha. maine kaha ke (eik hi ( kapda tha (is tarah na lapet'ta to kya karta (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo kushaada ho to usey achi tarah lapet liya kar aur agar tang ho to usko tehband ke taur par baandh liya kar."
362,kai aadmi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bachchon ki tarah apni gardanon par azaarein baandhey huey Namaz padhtey they aur aurton ko (aap ke zamaney mein) hukm tha ke apne saron ko (sajdey se) us waqt tak na uthayen jab tak mard seedhey ho kar baith na jaaein.
363,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar ( jange-Tabook ( mein tha. aap ne aik mauqe par farmaya, Mughira ! pani ki chhaagal utha ley. maine usey utha liya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaley aur meri nazron se chhup gaey. aap ne qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki. us waqt aap shaami jubba pahney huey they. aap hath kholney ke liye aasteen uper chadhai chahtey they lekin wo tang thi isliye aasteen ke andar se hath bahar nikala . maine aap ke hathon par pani dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ke wuzu ki tarah wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya. phir Namaz padhi."
364,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( nabwooat se pahley) Kaba ke liye Quraish ke sath patthar dho rahe they. us waqt aap tehband baandhey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha Abbas ne kaha ke bhatijey kyon nahi tum tehband khol letey aur usey patthar ke nichey apne kaandhey par rakh letey (taake tum par aasani ho jaey) Jaabir ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tehband khol liya aur kaandhey par rakh liya. usi waqt ghashii kha kar gir padey. iske baad aap kabhi nangey nahi dekhey gaey.
365,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khada hua aur us ne sirf aik kapda pahan kar Namaz padhney ke barey mein sawal kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum sab hi logon ke paas 2 kapdey ho saktey hain? phir ( yahi masla ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) se aik shakhs ne puchha to unhon-ne kaha jab Allah Taala ne tumhen faraghat di hai to tum bhi faraghat ke sath raho. aadmi ko chahiye ke Namaz main apne kapdey ikattha kar ley , koi aadmi tehband aur chadar mein Namaz padhey , koi tehband aur qamees , koi tehband aur Quba mein, koi paa-jaama aur chadar mein, koi paa-jaama aur qamees mein, koi paa-jaama aur Quba mein, koi jaangiyaa aur Quba mein, koi jaangiyaa aur qamees mein Namaz padhey . Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey yad aata hai ke aap ne ye bhi kaha ke koi jaangiyaa aur chadar mein Namaz padhey ."
366,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aadmi ne puchha ke ehram baandhney waley ko kya pahannaa chahiye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke na qamees pahney na paa-jaama, na barish ka coat aur na aisa kapda jis mein zafran laga hua ho aur na waras laga hua kapda , phir agar kisi shakhs ko jootiyaan na milein (jin mein paon khula rehta ho ( wo mozey kaat kar pahan ley taake wo takhnon se nichey ho jayen aur ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne us hadis ko Naafe se bhi riwayat kya, unhon-ne aisa hi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi riwayat kya hai."
367,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sakht bakkal ki tarah kapda badan par lapet leney se mana farmaya aur isse bhi mana farmaya ke aadmi aik kapdey mein ehtibaa' (kapde me goth maare) karey aur uski sharmgah par alehda koi doosra kapda na ho.
368,"ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 tarah ki khareed-farokht se mana farmaya, aik to chhooney ki khareed se, doosrey phainkney ki khareed se aur ishtimaale-sammaa se (jiska bayan uper guzra (aur aik kapdey mein got mar kar baithney se."
369,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke us Haj ke mauqe par mujhey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne yaumun-nahar (zil-hijja ki dasween taareekh ( mein elaan karne walon ke sath bhejaa. taake ham Mina mein is baat ka elaan kar dein ke us saal ke baad koi mushrik Haj nahi kar sakta aur koi shakhs nangey ho kar Baitullah ka tawaaf nahi kar sakta. Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne kaha iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey bheja aur unhein hukm diya ke wo sura Bara't (Tauba) padh kar suna dein aur uske mzaameen ka aam elaan kar dein. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamarey sath nehar ke din Mina mein dasween taareekh ko ye sunaya ke aaj ke baad koi mushrik na Haj kar sakega aur na Baitullah ka tawaaf koi shakhs nangey hokar kar sakega.
370,"mein Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari ki khidmat mein hazir hua. wo aik kapda apne badan par lapetey huey Namaz padh rahe they, halanke unki chadar alag rakhi hui thi. jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to ham ne kaha aey abu-Adbullah! aap ki chadar rakhi hui hai aur aap (usey odhey baghair) Namaz padh rahe hain. unhon-ne farmaya, maine chaha ke tum jaisey jaahi log mujhey is tarah Namaz padhtey dekh lein, maine bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah aik kapdey mein Namaz padhtey dekha tha."
371,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Khaibar ki jang mein tashrif ley gaey. ham ne wahan fajr ki Namaz andherey hi mein padhi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sawar huey aur abu-Talha bhi sawar huey. mein abu-Talha ke peechhey betha hua tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni sawari ka rukh khaibar ki galiyon ki taraf kar diya. mera ghutna Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan se chhu jata tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni raan se tehband ko hataya . yahan tak ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shaffaaf aur safaid raanon ki safedi aur chamak dekhney laga. jab aap khaibar ki basti mein dakhil huey, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (Allaahu-akbar) Allah sabse bada hai, khaibar barbad ho gaya, jab ham kisi qaum ke aangan mein utar jayen to daraaey huey logon ki subah manhoos ho jati hai. aap ne ye teen martaba farmaya, usne kaha ke khaibar ke Yahudi log apne kaamon ke liye bahar nikley hi they ke wo chilla uthey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aan pahunchey aur Abdul-Azeez rawi ne kaha ke kuchh Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat karne waley hamarey sathiyon ne ( والخميس‏ (ka lafz bhi naql kya hai (yani wo chilla uthey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lashkar lekar pahunch gaey) to ham ne khaibar lad kar fateh kar liya aur qaidi jama kiye gaey. phir Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! qaidiyon mein se koi baandi mujhey inayat kijiye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao koi baandi ley lo. unhon-ne Safiya binte- huyii ko ley liya. phir aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! Safiya jo Qureza aur nazeer ke sardaar ki beti hain, unhein aap ne Dahiya ko de diya. wo to sirf aap hi ke liye munasib thin. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Dahiya ko Safiya ke sath bulao , wo laey gaey. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to farmaya ke qaidiyon mein se koi aur baandi ley lo. rawi ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya ko aazad kar diya aur unhein apne nikah mein ley liya. Sabit Bunani ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke abu-Hamza ! unka mehar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya rakha tha? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke khud unhein ki aazadi unka mehar tha aur usi par aap ne nikah kya. phir rastey hi mein Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida ( ne unhein dulhan banaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas raat ke waqt bhejaa. ab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dulhaa they, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiske paas bhi kuchh khaney ki cheez ho to yahan laey. aapne aik chamdey ka dastar-khuwaan bichhaayaa. kuchh sahaba khajoor laaey, kuchh ghii, Abdul-Azeez ne kaha ke mera khayal hai Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne sattu ka bhi zikr kya. phir logon ne unka halwa bana liya. ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka walima tha."
372,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fajr ki Namaz padhtey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein kai musalman auratein apni chaadrein odhey huey Namaz mein Sharik hotin, phir apne gharon ko wapas chali jati thin, us waqt unhein koi pehchan nahi sakta tha."
373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik chadar mein Namaz padhi. jis mein naqsh w nigaar they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik martaba dekha. phir jab Namaz se farigh huey to farmaya ke meri ye chadar abu-Jaheem ( Aamir-bin-Huzaifa (ke paas ley jao aur unki anbjaaniya wali chadar ley aao, kyonke us chadar ne abhi Namaz se mujh ko ghaafil kar diya aur Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main Namaz mein iske naqsh w nigaar dekh raha tha, isliye main dara ke kahin ye mujhey ghaafil na kar de."
374,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aik rangeen baareek parda tha jisey unhon-ne apne ghar ke aik taraf parde ke liye latkaa diya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere samney se apna ye parda hata do. kyonke is par naqsh wali tasweerein barabar meri Namaz mein khalal paida kati rahi hain.
375,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik resham ki Quba tohfe mein di gaee. usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pehna aur Namaz padhi, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz se farigh huey to badi tezi ke sath usey utaar diya. maano Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey pahan kar na-gawari mehsus kar rahe they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye parhezgaaron ke laaiq nahi hai."
376,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik surkh chamdey ke kheme mein dekha aur maine ye bhi dekha ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wuzu kara rahe hain aur har shakhs aap ke wuzu ka pani hasil karne ke liye aik doosrey se aagey badhney ki koshish kar raha hai. agar kisi ko thoda sa bhi pani mil jata to wo usey apne uper mal leta aur agar koi pani na pa sakta to apne sathi ke hath ki tarii hi hasil karne ki koshish karta. phir maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhon-ne apni aik barchhi uthai jiske nichey lohey ka phal laga hua tha aur usey unhon-ne gaad diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (dere mein se) aik surkh poshak pahney huey tehband uthaey huey bahar tashrif laey aur barchhi ki taraf munh karke logon ko 2 rakaat Namaz padhai, maine dekha ke aadmi aur janwar barchhi ke parey se guzar rahe they."
377,"mimbare-nabawii kis cheez ka tha. aap ne farmaya ke ab (Islami duniya mein) iske mutaalliq mujh se zyada jaanney wala koi baqi nahi raha hai. member Ghaaba ke jhaau se bana tha. falan aurat ke ghulam falan ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye banaya tha. jab wo taiyaar karke (masjid mein) rakha gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par khadey huey aur aap ne qible ki taraf apna munh kya aur takbeer kahi aur log aap ke peechhey khadey ho gaey. phir aap ne Quran Majeed ki aayatein padhein aur rukoo kya. aap ke peechhey tamam log bhi rukoo mein chaley gaey. phir aap ne apna sar uthaya . phir usi haalat mein aap ultey paon peechhey hatey . phir zameen par sajda kya. phir member par dobara tashrif laey aur qirat rukoo ki, phir rukoo se sar uthaya aur qibla hi ki taraf rukh kiye huey peechhey lautey aur zameen par sajda kya. ye hai member ka qissa. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha ke mujh se imam Ahmad-bin-Hanbal ne us hadis ko poochha. Ali ne kaha ke mera maqsad ye hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz mein logon se oonchey maqam par khadey huey they isliye usmein koi harj na hona chahiye ke imam muqtadiyon se unchi jagah par khada ho. Ali-bin madeenii kehtey hain ke maine imam Ahmad-bin-Hanbal se kaha ke Sufiyan-bin-Uena se ye hadis aksar poochhi jati thi, aap ne bhi ye hadis unse suni hai to unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi."
378,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( 5 H mein) apne ghodey se gir gaey they. jis se aap ki pindlii ya kandhaa zakhmi ho gaey aur aap ne aik mahiney tak apni beeviyon ke paas na janey ki qism khaaii. aap apne baalaakhaane par baith gaey. jiske zeeney khajoor ke tanon se banaey gaey they. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mizaaj pursi ko aaey. aap ne unhein baith kar Namaz padhai aur wo khadey they. jab aap ne salam phera to farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski pairwi ki jaey. to jab wo takbeer kahey to tum bhi takbeer kaho aur jab wo rukoo mein jaey to tum bhi rukoo mein jao aur jab wo sajda karey to tum bhi sajda karo aur agar khadey ho kar tumhen Namaz padhaaey to tum bhi khadey ho kar Namaz padho aur aap untees din baad nichey tashrif laaey, to logon ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! aap ne to aik mahina ke liye qism khaaii thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye mahina untees din ka hai."
379,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey aur haaiza honey ke bawajud mein unke samney hoti, aksar jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kapda mujhey chhu jata. unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( khajoor ke patton se baney huey aik chhotey se) musalley par Namaz padhtey they."
380,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khana taiyaar karke khaney ke liye bulaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaney ke baad farmaya ke aao tumhen Namaz padha dun. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine apne ghar se aik boriyaa uthaya jo kasarat istemal se kala ho gaya tha. maine is par pani chhidkaa. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye (usi boriye par) khadey huey aur main aur aik yateem (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghulam Abu-Zameera ke ladkey Zameera) aap ke peechhey saf baandh kar khadey ho gaey aur boodhi aurat (Anas ki nani mulaika) hamarey peechhey khadi huin. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padhai aur wapas ghar tashrif ley gaey.
381,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda gaah (yani chhotey musalley) par Namaz padha kartey they.
382,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey so jati aur mere paon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qibla mein hotey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey, to mere paon ko aahista se daba detey. main apne paon samet leti aur aap jab khadey ho jatey to main unhein phir phaila deti. un dinon gharon mein charagh bhi nahi hua kartey they."
383,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar ke bichhoney par Namaz padhtey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur qible ke darmyan is tarah leti hotiin jaisey (namaz ke liye) janaaza rakha jata hai.
384,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us bichhoney par Namaz padhtey jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sotey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur qible ke darmyan us bistar par leti rehtin.
385,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey they. phir sakht garmi ki wjah se koi koii ham mein se apne kapdey ka kinara sajdey ki jagah rakh leta .
386,kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jootiyaan pahan kar Namaz padhtey they? to unhon-ne farmaya ke haan!.
387,"maine Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, unhon-ne peshab kya phir wuzu kya aur apne mozon par masah kya. phir khadey huey aur) mozon samet ( Namaz padhi. aap se jab iske mutaalliq puchha gaya, to farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisa hi kartey dekha hai. Ibrahim Nakhai ne kaha ke ye hadis logon ki nazar mein bahut pasandida thi kyonke Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) aakhir mein Islam laey they."
388,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wuzu karaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne mozon par masah kya aur Namaz padhi.
389,"unhon-ne aik shakhs ko dekha jo rukoo aur sajda poori tarah nahi karta tha. jab us ne apni Namaz poori kar li to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tum ne Namaz hi nahi padhi. abu-Waeil rawi ne kaha, mein khayal karta hun ke Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi farmaya ke agar to aisi hi Namaz par mar jata to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat par nahi marta."
390,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz padhtey to apne baazuon ke darmyan is qadr kushadgi kar detey ke donon baghlon ki safedi zahir honey lagti thi aur Leis ne yun kaha ke mujh se Jafar bin Rabeea ne isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
391,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jisne hamari tarah Namaz padhi aur hamari tarah qible ki taraf munh kya aur hamarey zabiha ko khaya to wo musalman hai jiske liye Allah aur uske rasool ki panah hai. to tum Allah ke sath uski di hui panah mein khayanat na karo."
392,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon ke sath jang karun yahan tak ke wo ( لا إله إلا الله ( kahein. to jab wo iska iqrar kar lein aur hamari tarah Namaz padhney lagein aur hamarey qible ki taraf Namaz mein munh karein aur hamarey zabiha ko khaney lagein to unka khoon aur unke amwaal ham par haram ho gaey. magar kisi haq ke badley aur (baatin mein) unka hisab Allah par rahega.
393,aey abu-Hamza ! aadmi ki jaan aur maal par zyadti ko kya cheezein haram karti hain? to unhon-ne farmaya ke jisne gawahi di ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur hamarey qible ki taraf munh kya aur hamari Namaz ki tarah Namaz padhi aur hamarey zabiha ko khaya to wo musalman hai. phir iske wahi huquq hain jo aam musalmanon ke hain aur uski wahi zimma daariyaan hain jo aam musalmanon par hain.
394,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tum qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye jao to us waqt na qible ki taraf munh karo aur na peeth karo. balke mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf us waqt apna munh kar liya karo. Abu-Ayub ne farmaya ke ham jab Sham (Syria) mein aaey to yahan ke baitul-khala qibla rukh baney huey they (jab ham qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye jatey ( to ham mud jatey aur izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah se istighfar kartey they aur Zohri ne Ata se us hadis ko isi tarah riwayat kya. usmein yun hai ke Ata ne kaha maine Abu-Ayub se suna, unhon-ne isi tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
395,"aik aisey shakhs ke barey mein puchha jisne Baitullah ka tawaaf umre ke liye kya lekin Safa aur Marwa ki saee nahi ki, kya aisa shakhs (baitullaah ke tawaaf ke baad) apni biwi se sohbat kar sakta hai? aap ne jawab diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aap ne saat (7) martaba Baitullah ka tawaaf kya aur maqaame-Ibraaheem ke paas 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir Safa aur Marwa ki saee ki aur tumharey liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi behtreen namoona hai.'' (Ahzaab : 21)"
396,bhi ye masla puchha to aap ne bhi yahi farmaya ke wo biwi ke qareeb bhi us waqt tak na jaey jab tak Safa aur Marwa ki saee na kar ley.
397,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga, aey lo ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aan pahunchey aur aap Kaba ke andar dakhil ho gaey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main jab aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba se nikal chukey they, maine dekha ke Bilal donon darwazon ke samney khadey hain. maine Bilal se puchha ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ke andar Namaz padhi hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan! 2 rakaat un 2 sutunon ke darmyan padhi thin, jo Kaba mein dakhil hotey waqt baain taraf bane hue hain. phir jab bahar tashrif laey to Kaba ke samney 2 rakaat Namaz ada farmai."
398,jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke andar tashrif le gaey to iske charon konon mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aur Namaz nahi padhi. phir jab bahar tashrif laey to 2 rakaat Namaz Kaba ke samney padhi aur farmaya ke yahi qibla hai.
399,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 16 ya 17 maah tak baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke namazein padhein aur rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (dil se) chahtey they ke Kaba ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhein. aakhir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmai : ham aap ka aasman ki taraf baar-baar chehra uthana dekhtey hain. phir aap ne Kaba ki taraf munh kar liya aur ahmaqon ne jo Yahudi they kehna shuru kya ke unhein agley qibla se kis cheez ne pher diya. aap farma dijiye ke Allah hi ki milkiyat hai mashriq aur maghrib, Allah jis ko chahta hai seedhey rastey ki hidayat kar deta hai. (jab qibla badla to ( aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi phir Namaz ke baad wo chala aur Ansar ki aik jamat par uska guzar hua jo Asr ki Namaz baitul-maqdis ki taraf munh karke padh rahe they. us shakhs ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wo Namaz padhi hai jis mein aap ne maujooda qibla (ka'be) ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhi hai. phir wo jamat (namaz ki haalat mein hi) mud gaee aur Kaba ki taraf munh kar liyaa."
400,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par chahe uska rukh kisi taraf ho ( nafl ( Namaz padhtey they lekin jab farz Namaz padhna chahtey to sawari se utar jatey aur qible ki taraf munh karke Namaz padhtey.
401,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai. Ibrahim ne kaha mujhey nahi malum ke Namaz mein zyadti hui ya kamii. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke ya Rasulullah! kya Namaz mein koi nayaa hukm aaya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aakhir kya baat hai? logon ne kaha aapne itni-itnii rakatein padhi hain. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon paon pherey aur qible ki taraf munh kar liya aur (saho ke) 2 sajdey kiye aur salam pheraa. phir hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke agar Namaz mein koi nayaa hukm nazil hua hota to main tumhen pahley hi zaroor keh deta lekin main to tumharey hi jaisa aadmi hon, jis tarah tum bhooltey ho mein bhi bhool jata hun. isliye jab main bhool jaya karun to tum mujhey yad dilaya karo aur agar kisi ko Namaz mein shak ho jaey to us waqt theek baat soch ley aur usi ke mutabiq Namaz poori karey phir salam pher kar do sajdey ( saho ke) kar ley."
402,"meri teen baton mein jo mere munh se nikla mere rab ne waisaa hi hukm farmaya, maine kaha tha ke ya Rasulullah ! agar ham maqaame-Ibraaheem ko Namaz padhney ki jagah bana saktey to achchha hota. is par ye aayat nazil hui. ''aur tum maqaame-Ibraaheem ko Namaz padhney ki jagah bana lo '' dusri aayat parda ke barey mein hai. maine kaha tha ke ya Rasulullah kash! ! aap apni aurton ko parde ka hukm detey, kyonke unse achchhey aur burey har tarah ke log baat kartey hain. is par parde ki aayat nazil hui aur aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan josh w kharosh mein aap ki khidmat mein ittifaq karke kuchh mataalbaat (maangein) lekar hazir huin. maine unse kaha ke ho sakta hai ke Allah paak tumhen talaaq dila dein aur tumharey badley tum se behtar Muslima beeviyan apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko inayat karein, to ye aayat nazil hui ( عسى ربه إن طلقكن أن يبدله أزواجا خيرا منكن‏ (aur Saeed-ibn-abii-Maryam ne kaha ke mujhey Yahya bin Ayub ne khabar di, kaha ke ham se Humaid ne bayan kya, kaha maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis suni."
403,"log Quba mein fajr ki Namaz padh rahe they ke itney mein aik aaney wala aaya. usne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kal wahi nazil hui hai aur unhein Kaba ki taraf (namaz mein) munh karne ka hukm ho gaya hai. chunanche un logon ne bhi Kaba ki taraf munh kar liye jabke us waqt wo Sham (Syria) ki taraf munh kiye huey they, isliye wo sab Kaba ki taraf ghoom gaey."
404,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( bhooley se) Zohar ki Namaz (eik martaba ( panch rakaat padhi hain. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke phir aap ne apne paon mod liye aur) saho ke) 2 sajdey kiye.
405,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qible ki taraf ( diwar par) balgham dekha, jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na-gawar guzra aur ye na-gawari Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par dikhai dene lagi phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur khud apne hath se usey khurch daala aur farmaya ke jab koi shakhs Namaz ke liye khada hota hai to maano wo apne rab ke sath sargoshi karta hai, ya yun farmaya ke uska rab uske aur qible ke darmyan hota hai. isliye koi shakhs (namaz mein apne) qible ki taraf na thookey. albatta baain taraf ya apne qadmon ke nichey thook sakta hai. phir aap ne apni chadar ka kinara liya, is par thooka phir usko ulat palat kya aur farmaya, ya is tarah kar liya karo."
406,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qibley ki diwar par thook dekha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khurch daala phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) logon se khitab kya aur farmaya ke jab koi shakhs Namaz mein ho to apne munh ke samney na thookey kyonke Namaz mein munh ke samney izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah hota hai."
407,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qible ki diwar par raint ya thook ya balgham dekha to usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khurch dala.
408,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ki diwar par balgham dekha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kankari li aur usey saaf kar diya. phir farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs thookey to usey apne munh ke samney ya daain taraf nahi thookna chahiye, albatta baain taraf ya apne paon ke nichey thook ley."
409,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ki diwar par balgham dekha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kankari li aur usey saaf kar diya. phir farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs thookey to usey apne munh ke samney ya daain taraf nahi thookna chaahiye, albatta baain taraf ya apne paon ke nichey thook ley."
410,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kankari se usey khurch daala aur farmaya agar tum mein se kisi ko thookna ho to usey apne chehrey ke samney ya apne daain taraf na thooka karo, albatta apne baain taraf ya apne baain qadam ke nichey thook saktey ho."
411,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kankari se usey khurch daala aur farmaya agar tum mein se kisi ko thookna ho to usey apne chehrey ke samney ya apne daain taraf na thooka karo, albatta apne baain taraf ya apne baain qadam ke nichey thook saktey ho."
412,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tum apne samney ya apni daain taraf na thooka karo, albatta baain taraf ya baain qadam ke nichey thook saktey ho."
413,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya momin jab Namaz mein hota hai to wo apne rab se sargoshi karta hai. isliye wo apne samney ya daain taraf na thookey, haan baain taraf ya paon ke nichey thook ley."
414,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid ke qible ki diwar par balgham dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kankari se khurch dala. phir farmaya ke koi shakhs samney ya daain taraf na thookey , albatta baain taraf ya baaein paon ke nichey thook lena chahiye dusri riwayat mein Zohri se yun hai ke unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman se Abu-Saeed Khudri ke waaste se isi tarah ye hadis suni."
415,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke masjid mein thookna gunah hai aur iska kaffara usey ( zameen mein) chipa dena hai.
416,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab koi shakhs Namaz ke liye khada ho to samney na thookey kyonke wo jab tak apni Namaz ki jagah mein hota hai to Allah Taala se sargoshi karta rehta hai aur daain taraf bhi na thookey kyonke us taraf farishta hota hai, haan baain taraf ya qadam ke nichey thook ley aur usey mitti mein chipa de."
417,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qible ki taraf ( diwar par) balgham dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud usey khurch daala aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki naakhushii ko mehsus kya gaya ya ( rawi ne is tarah bayan kya ke) uski wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shadeed na-gawari ko mehsus kya gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab koi shakhs Namaz ke liye khada hota hai to wo apne rab se sargoshi karta hai, ya ye ke iska rab iske aur qible ke darmyan hota hai. isliye qible ki taraf na thooka karo, albatta baain taraf ya qadam ke nichey thook liya karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni chadar ka aik kona ( kinara ( liya, usmein thooka aur chadar ki aik teh ko dusri teh par pher liya aur farmaya, ya is tarah kar liya kare."
418,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tumhara ye khayal hai ke mera munh (namaz mein) qible ki taraf hai, Allah ki qism mujh se na tumhara khushoo chhiptaa hai na rukoo , main apni peeth ke peechhey se tum ko dekhta rehta hun."
419,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik martaba Namaz padhai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par chadhey, phir Namaz ke baab main aur rukoo ke baab mein farmaya main tumhen peechhey se bhi isi tarah dekhta rehta hon jaisey ab samney se dekh raha hun."
420,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ghodon ki jinhein (jihad ke liye) taiyaar kya gaya tha maqam hafiya se daud karaaii, us daud ki had saniiya al-wada' thi aur jo ghodey abhi taiyaar nahi huey they unki daud saniiya al-wada' se masjid bani zuraiq tak karaai . Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi us ghud-daud mein shirkat ki thi."
421,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Bahrain se raqam aai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey masjid mein daal do aur ye raqam us tamam raqam se zyada thi jo ab tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aa chuki thi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif laey aur uski taraf koi tawajjoh nahi farmai, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz poori kar chukey to aa kar maal ( raqam (ke paas baith gaey aur usey taqseem karna shuru farma diya. us waqt jisey bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekhtey usey ata farma detey. itney mein Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hazir huey aur boley ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey bhi ata kiijiye kyonke maine ( jange-badr mein) apna bhi fidya diya tha aur Aqeel ka bhi (is liye mein zere-baar hun) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ley lijiye . unhon-ne apne kapdey mein rupya bhar liya aur usey uthaney ki koshish ki lekin (wazan ki zyadti ki wjah se) wo na utha sakey aur kehney lagey ya Rasulullah ! kisi ko farmaiye ke wo uthaney mein meri madad kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi (ye nahi ho sakta ( unhon-ne kaha ke phir aap hi uthwa dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par bhi inkar kya, tab Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein se thoda sa gira diya aur baqi ko uthaney ki koshish ki, ( lekin ab bhi na utha sakey ( phir farmaya ke ya Rasulullah ! kisi ko meri madad karne ka hukm dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne inkar farmaya to unhon-ne kaha ke phir aap hi uthwa dijiye. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se bhi inkar kya, tab unhon-ne usmein se thoda sa rupya gira diya aur usey utha kar apne kaandhey par rakh liya aur chalney lagey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unki us hirs par itna tajjub hua ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tak unki taraf dekhtey rahe jab tak wo hamari nazron se ghayab nahi ho gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi wahan se us waqt tak na uthey jab tak ke aik chawannii bhi baqi rahi."
422,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid mein paya , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aur bhi kai log they. main khada ho gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se puchha ke kya tujh ko abu-Talha ne bheja hai? maine kaha ji haan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha khaney ke liye? ( bulaya hai) maine kaha ke ji haan ! tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne qareeb maujood logon se farmaya ke chalo , sab hazraat chalney lagey aur main unke aagey-aagey chal raha tha."
423,"aik shakhs ne kaha, ya Rasulullah ! us shakhs ke baare mein farmaiye jo apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko) bura kaam kartey huey) dekhta hai, kya usey mar daaley? aakhir us mard ne apni biwi ke sath masjid mein liaan kya aur us waqt main maujood tha."
424,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke tum apne ghar mein kahan pasand kartey ho ke tumharey liye Namaz padhun . Utban ne bayan kya ke maine aik jagah ki taraf ishara kya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne takbeer kahi aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey saf baandhii phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz ( nafl ( padhai.
425,"Utban bin Malik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi aur jange-badr ke hazir honey walon mein se they, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ya Rasulullah ! meri beenaaii mein kuchh farq aa gaya hai aur main apni qaum ke logon ko Namaz padhaayaa karta hun lekin jab barsat ka mausam aata hai to mere aur meri qaum ke darmyan jo wadi hai wo bhar jati hai aur bahney lag jati hai aur main unhein Namaz padhaaney ke liye masjid tak nahi ja sakta ya Rasulullah ! meri khahish hai ke aap mere ghar tashrif laaein aur (kisi jagah ( Namaz padh dein taake main usey Namaz padhney ki jagah bana loon. rawi ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Utban se farmaya, insha-Allah taala mein tumhari us khahish ko pura karunga . Utban ne kaha ke (doosrey din) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) jab din chadhaa to donon tashrif ley aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar aaney ki ijazat chaahii, maine ijazat de di. jab aap ghar mein tashrif laey to baithey bhi nahi aur puchha ke tum apne ghar ke kis hisse mein mujh se Namaz padhney ki khahish rakhtey ho. Utban ne kaha ke maine ghar mein aik koney ki taraf ishara kya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (is jagah ( khadey huey aur takbeer kahi ham bhi aap ke peechhey khadey ho gaey aur saf baandhii to aap ne 2 rakaat ( nafl ( Namaz padhai phir salam phera . Utban ne kaha ke ham ne aapko thodi der ke liye rokaa aur aap ki khidmat mein haleem pesh kya jo aap hi ke liye taiyaar kya gaya tha. Utban ne kaha ke mahalla walon ka aik majma' ghar mein lag gaya aur majme' mein se aik shakhs bola ke Malik bin Dukhshan ya (ye kaha ( ibne-Dakhshan dikhai nahi deta. is par kisi doosrey ne keh diya ke wo to munafiq hai jisey Allah aur rasool se koi mohabbat nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sun kar farmaya aisa mat kaho , kya tum dekhtey nahi ke usne ( لا إله إلا الله ( kaha hai aur us se maqsud khalis Allah ki razaamandii hasil karna hai. tab munaafiqat ka ilzam lagaaney wala bola ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai ham to bazahir uski taujeehaat aur dosti munaafiqon hi ke sath dekhtey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne ( لا إله إلا الله ( kehney waley par agar iska maqsad khalis Allah ki raza hasil karna ho dozakh ki aag haram kar di hai. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke phir maine Mehmood se sun kar Husain-bin-Muhammad Ansari se jo banu-Saalim ke sharif logon mein se hain (is hadis) ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne uski tasdeeq ki aur kaha ke Mehmood sachcha hai."
426,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne tamam kaamon mein jahan tak mumkin hota daain taraf se shuru karne ko pasand farmatey they. tahaarat ke waqt bhi, kangha karne aur jootaa pahnney mein bhii."
427,Umme-Habiba aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) donon ne aik kaleesaa ka zikr kya jisey unhon-ne Habsha mein dekha to usmein moortein ( tasweerein ( thin. unhon-ne iska tazkira Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unka ye qaayda tha ke agar unmein koi neku-kaar ( nek ( shakhs mar jata to wo log uski qabr par masjid banatey aur is mein yahi moortein ( tasweerein ( bana detey to ye log Allah ki dargaah mein qiyamat ke din tamam makhlooq mein burey hongey.
428,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to yahan ke buland hisse mein bani Amr-bin-Auf ke yahan aap utrey aur yahan chobis raatein qiyam farmaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Najjaar ko bula bhejaa, to wo log talwaarein latkaey huey aaey. Anas ne kaha, maano meri nazron ke samney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par tashrif farma hain, jabke Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey baithey huey hain aur banu-Najjaar ke log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charon taraf hain. yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Ayub ke ghar ke samney utrey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye pasand kartey they ke jahan bhi Namaz ka waqt aa jaey fauran Namaz ada kar lein. aap bakriyon ke baadon mein bhi Namaz padh letey they, phir aap ne yahan masjid banaaney ke liye hukm farmaya, chunanche banu-Najjaar ke logon ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulwa kar farmaya ke aey banu-Najjaar ! tum apne us baagh ki qeemat mujh se ley lo. unhon-ne jawab diya, nahi ya Rasulullah! uski qeemat ham sirf Allah se maangtey hain. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main jaisa ke tumhen bata raha tha yahan mushrekeen ki qabrein thin, us baagh mein aik weeraan jagah thi aur kuchh khajoor ke darakht bhi they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mushrekeen ki qabron ko Ukhadwaa diya weeraane ko saaf aur barabar karaya aur darakhton ko katwaa kar unki lakdiyon ko masjid ke qible ki taraf bichhaa diya aur pattharon ke zariey unhein mazbut bana diya. sahaba patthar uthatey huey rajz padhtey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unke sath they aur ye keh rahe they ke aey Allaah! aakhirat ke fayda ke ilawa aur koi fayda nahi to Ansar w muhajireen ki maghfirat farmaanaa."
429,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakriyon ke baadon mein Namaz padhtey they, Abu-Tayyah ya Shoba ne kaha, phir maine Anas ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bakriyon ke baade (goats pen) mein masjid ki tameer se pahley Namaz padha kartey they."
430,maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne oont ki taraf Namaz padhtey dekha aur unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah padhtey dekha tha.
431,"suraj gehen hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi aur farmaya ke mujhey ( aaj ( dozakh dikhai gaee, us se zyada bhayanak manzar maine kabhi nahi dekha."
432,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya apne gharon mein bhi namazein padha karo aur unhein bilkul maqbara na bana lo.
433,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, un azab walon ke aasaar se agar tumhara guzar ho to rotey huey guzro, agar tum us mauqe par ro na sako to unse guzro hi nahi. aisa na ho ke tum par bhi unka sa azab aa jaey."
434,Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik girja (church) ka zikr kya jis ko unhon-ne habsh ke mulk mein dekha iska naam Mariya tha. usmein jo moortein dekhi thin wo bayan kin. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aisey log they ke agar unmein koi nek banda (ya ye farmaya ke) nek aadmi mar jata to uski qabr par masjid banatey aur is mein ye but (moorti) rakhtey. ye log Allah ke nazdeek saari makhlooqat se badtar hain.
435,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maut ke marz mein mubtala huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar ko baar-baar chehrey par daaltey. jab kuchh fayda hota to apne Mubarak chehrey se chadar hata detey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi iztiraab w pareshani ki haalat mein farmaya, yahood w nasara par Allah ki phitkar ho ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masjid bana liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye farma kar ummat ko aisey kaamon se daraatey they."
436,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maut ke marz mein mubtala huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar ko baar-baar chehrey par daaltey. jab kuchh fayda hota to apne Mubarak chehrey se chadar hata detey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi bechaini w pareshani ki haalat mein farmaya, yahood w nasara par Allah ki phitkar ho ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masjid bana liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye farma kar ummat ko aisey kaamon se daraatey they."
437,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, yahudiyon par Allah ki laanat ho unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko masaajid bana liya."
438,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mujhey panch aisi cheezein ata ki gaee hain jo mujh se pahley anbiya ko nahi di gaee thin. (1) aik mahiney ki raah se mera raub daal kar meri madad ki gaee. (2) mere liye tamam zameen mein Namaz padhney aur paakii hasil karne ki ijazat hai. isliye meri ummat ke jis aadmi ki Namaz ka waqt ( jahan bhi) aa jaey usey ( wahin ( Namaz padh leni chahiye (3) mere liye maale-ghanimat halal kya gaya. (4) pahley anbiya khas apni qaumon ki hidayat ke liye bhejey jatey they. lekin mujhey duniya ke tamam insanon ki hidayat ke liye bheja gaya hai. (5) mujhey shafaat ata ki gaee hai."
439,"Arab ke kisi qabeele ki aik kali londi thi. unhon-ne usey aazad kar diya tha aur wo unhiin ke sath rehti thi. usne bayan kya ke aik baar unki aik ladki (jo dulhan thi) nahaaney ko nikli , iska kamar band surkh tasmon ka tha us ne wo kamar band utaar kar rakh diya ya iske badan se gir gaya. phir us taraf se aik cheel guzri jahan kamar band padaa tha. cheel usey ( surkh rang ki wjah se) gosht samajh kar jhapat ley gaee. baad mein qabila walon ne usey bahut talash kya, lekin kahin na mila. un logon ne uski tohmat mujh par laga di aur meri talashi leni shuru kar di. yahan tak ke unhon-ne uski sharmgah tak ki talashi li. usne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism mein unke sath usi haalat mein khadi thi ke wahi cheel aai aur usne unka wo kamar band gira diya. wo unke samney hi giraa. maine (usey dekh kar) kaha yahi to tha jiski tum mujh par tohmat lagaatey they. tum logon ne mujh par iska ilzam lagaya tha halanke main us se paak thi. yahi to hai wo kamarband! us (laundii) ne kaha ke iske baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur Islam laaii. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke uske liye masjide-Nabawi mein aik bada khema laga diya gaya. (ya ye kaha ke) chhota sa khema laga diya gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke wo londi mere paas aati aur mujh se baatein kya karti thi. jab bhi wo mere paas aati to ye zaroor kehti ke kamarband ka din hamarey rab ki ajeeb nishaniyon mein se hai. usi ne mujhey kufr ke mulk se nijat di. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke maine usse kaha, aakhir baat kya hai? jab bhi tum mere paas baithtii ho to ye baat zaroor kehti ho. aap ne bayan kya ke phir us ne mujhey ye qissa sunaya."
440,wo apni naujawaanii mein jabke unke biwi bachchey nahi they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein soyaa kartey they.
441,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif laey dekha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ghar mein maujood nahi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey chacha ke betey kahan hain? unhon-ne bataya ke mere aur unke darmyan kuchh na-gawari pesh aa gaee aur wo mujh par khafa ho kar kahin bahar chale gaey hain aur mere yahan qailula bhi nahi kya hai. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs se kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko talash karo ke kahan hain? wo aaey aur bataya ke masjid mein soey huey hain. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) letey huey they, chadar aap ke pahlu se gir gaee thi aur jism par mitti lag gaee thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jism se dhool jhaad rahe they aur farma rahe they utho abu-Turaab utho."
442,"aap ne farmaya ke maine 70 ashabe-Suffa ko dekha ke unmein koi aisa na tha jiske paas chadar ho. faqat tehband hota, ya raat ko odhney ka kapda jinhein ye log apni gardanon se baandh letey. ye kapdey kisi ke aadhi pindlii tak aatey aur kisi ke takhnon tak. ye hazraat un kapdon ko us khayal se ke kahin sharmgah na khul jaey apne hathon se sametey rahtey they."
443,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt masjid mein tashrif farma they. Misar ne kaha mera khayal hai ke Maharib ne chasht ka waqt bataya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (pahley ( 2 rakaat Namaz padh aur mera Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kuchh qarz tha. jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ada kya aur zyada hi diya.
444,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tum mein se koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to baithney se pahley 2 rakaat Namaz padh ley.
445,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab tak tum apne musalley par jahan tum ne Namaz padhi thi, baithey raho aur hawa khaarij na karo to malaaika tum par barabar durood bhejtey rahtey hain. kehtey hain ( اللهم اغفر له اللهم ارحمه ( ''aey Allaah! uski maghfirat kijiye aey Allaah! is par raham kiijiye.'"
446,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein masjide-Nabawi kachchi enton se banai gaee thi. uski chhat khajoor ki shakhon ki thi aur sutoon usi ki kadiyon ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein kisi qism ki zyadti nahi ki. albatta umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey badhaya aur uski tameer Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki banai hui buniyaadon ke mutabiq kachchi enton aur khajooron ki shakhon se ki aur uske sutoon bhi kadiyon hi ke rakhey. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski Imaarat ko badal diya aur usmein bahut si zyadti ki. uski diwarein naqsh hue pattharon aur chooney se banain. iske sutoon bhi naqsh hue pattharon se banwaey aur chhat sagwan se banai.
447,"Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein jao aur unki hadison suno . ham gaey. dekha ke abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) apne baagh ko durust kar rahe they. ham ko dekh kar aap ne apni chadar sanbhaalii aur gote mar kar baith gaey. phir ham se hadis bayan karne lagey. jab masjide-Nabawi ke banaaney ka zikr aaya to aap ne bataya ke ham to (masjid ke banaaney mein hissey letey waqt) eik-eik iint uthaatey. lekin Ammar 2-2 enetein utha rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to unke badan se mitti jhadney lagey aur farmaya, afsos ! Ammar ko aik baaghii jamat qatl karegii. jisey Ammar jannat ki dawat dengey aur wo jamat Ammar ko jahannam ki dawat de rahi hogi. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke main fitnon se Allah ki panah mangta hun."
448,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aurat ke paas aik aadmi bheja ke wo apne badhi ghulam se kahey ke mere liye ( member ( lakdiyon ke takhton se bana de jin par main betha karun.
449,aik aurat ne kaha ya Rasulullah (sl)! kya main aap ke liye koi aisi cheez na bana dun jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) betha karein. mera aik badhi ghulam bhi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar to chahey to member banwaa de.
450,"masjide-Nabawi ki tameer ke mutaalliq logon ki baton ko sun kar aap ne farmaya ke tum logon ne bahut zyada baatein ki hain. halanke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke jisne masjid banai Bukair ( rawi ( ne kaha mera khayal hai ke aap ne ye bhi farmaya ke us se maqsud Allah Taala ki raza ho, to Allah Taala aisa hi aik makan jannat mein uske liye banaega."
451,"aik shakhs masjide-Nabawi mein aaya aur wo teer liye huey tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke unki nokein thaamey rakho ."
452,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar koi shakhs hamari masaajid ya hamarey bazaron mein teer liye huey chaley to unke phal thaamey rahe, aisa na ho ke apne hathon se kisi musalman ko zakhmi kar de."
453,"main tumhen Allah ka waasta deta hun ke kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey huey nahi suna tha ke aey Hassan! Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se (mushrikon ko ashaar mein) jawab 2 aur aey Allaah! Hassan ki Rooh al-qudus ke zariey madad kar. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, haan (mein gawah hun. beshak maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai)."
454,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik din apne hujre ke darwazey par dekha. us waqt Habsha ke kuchh log masjid mein (nezon se) khel rahe they ( hathiyar chalaney ki mashq kar rahe they) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apni chadar mein chipa liya taake main unka khel dekh sakun .
455,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha jabke Habsha ke log chhotey nezon (bhaalon) se masjid mein khel rahe they.
456,"Barira (Raziallahu anhu)) londi ( unse apni kitabat ke barey mein madad leney aaein . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha tum chaho to main tumharey maalikon ko ye raqam de dun (aur tumhen aazad kara dun (aur tumhara 'walaa' ka talluq mujh se qaaim ho. aur Barira ke malikon ne kaha ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se) ke agar aap chaahein to jo qeemat baqi reh gaee hai wo de dein aur 'walaa' ka talluq ham se qaaim rahega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is baat ka zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum Barira ko khareed kar aazad karo aur 'walaa' ka talluq to usi ko hasil ho sakta hai jo aazad karaaey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey. Sufiyan ne (is hadis ko bayan kartey huey) aik martaba yun kaha ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par chadhey aur farmaya, un logon ka kya haal hoga jo aisi sharaait kartey hain jinka talluq kitabullah se nahi hai. jo shakhs bhi koi aisi shart karey jo kitabullah mein na ho uski koi haisiyat nahi hogi, agarche wo so martaba kar ley. us hadis ki riwayat Malik ne Yahya ke waaste se ki, wo Umra se ke Barira aur unhon-ne member par chadhney ka zikr nahi kya."
457,"unhon-ne masjide-Nabawi mein Abdullah ibne- abii-Hadrad se apne qarz ka taqaza kya aur donon ki guftgu buland awazon se honey lagi yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi apne hujrey se sun liya. aap parda hata kar bahar tashrif laey aur pukara . Ka'b, Kab (Raziallahu anhu) boley, ji ya Rasulullah ! ( hukm ( farmaiye kya irshad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne qarz mein se itna kam kar do. aap ka ishara tha ke aadha kam kar dein. unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah! maine (b-khushi) aisa kar diya. phir aap ne ibne-abi-Hadrad se farmaya, achchha ab utho aur iska qarz ada karo. (jo aadha maaf kar diya gaya hai)."
458,"aik habshi mard ya habshi aurat masjide-Nabawi mein jhaado diya karti thi. aik din uska intiqal ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske mutaalliq malum farmaya, logon ne bataya ke wo to intiqal kar gaee. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tum ne mujhey kyon na bataya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabr par tashrif laey aur is par Namaz padhi."
459,jab sura al-baqara ki sood se mutaalliq aayatein nazil huin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif le gaey aur un aayaton ki logon ke samney tilawat farmai. phir farmaya ke sharab ki tijarat haram hai.
460,"aik aurat ya mard masjid mein jhaado diya karta tha. abu-Raafe' ne kaha, mera khayal hai ke wo aurat hi thi. phir unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis naql ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski qabr par Namaz padhi."
461,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pichhli raat aik sarkash jin achcha mere paas aaya. ya isi tarah ki koi baat aap ne farmai, wo meri Namaz mein khalal daalnaa chahta tha. lekin Allah tabarak w taala ne mujhey is par qaabu de diya aur maine sochaa ke masjid ke kisi sutoon ke sath usey baandh dun taake subah ko tum sab bhi usey dekho. phir mujhey apne bhai Sulaiman ki ye dua yad aa gaee (jo sura Swaad mein hai) ''aey mere rab! mujhey aisa mulk ata karna jo mere baad kisi ko hasil na ho''. hadis ke rawi Rooh ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shaitan ko zaleel karke dhutkar diya."
462,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh sawar Najad ki taraf bhejey (jo tadaad mein tees they) ye log banu-Haneefa ke aik shakhs ko jiska naam Samaama-bin-Assaal tha pakad kar laey. unhon-ne usey masjid ke aik sutoon mein baandh diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur) teesrey roz Samama ki nek tabeeat dekh kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Samama ko chhod do. (rihaaii ke baad) wo masjide-Nabawi se qareeb aik khajoor ke baagh tak gaey aur wahan ghusl kya. phir masjid mein dakhil huey aur kaha (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأن محمدا رسول الله‏) main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad Allah ke sachey rasool hain.
463,Khandaq ki jang mein Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke bazu ki aik rag ( اکحل ( mein zakhm aaya tha. unke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein aik khema nasab kara diya taake aap qareeb reh kar unki dekh bhaal kya karein. masjid hi mein bani-Ghifar ke logon ka bhi aik khema tha. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke zakhm ka khoon (jo rag se kasrat se nikal raha tha) bah kar jab unke kheme tak pahuncha to wo dar gaey. unhon-ne kaha ke aey kheme waalo! tumhari taraf se ye kaisa khoon hamarey kheme tak aa raha hai. phir unhein malum hua ke ye khoon Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke zakhm se beh raha hai. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ka usi zakhm ki wjah se intiqal ho gaya.
464,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (hijjatul-wadaa mein) apni bimari ka shikwa kya (maine kaha ke main paidal tawaaf nahi kar saktii) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logon ke peechhey reh aur Sawar ho kar tawaaf kar. isliye maine tawaaf kya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Baitullah ke qareeb Namaz mein aayat (Sura Toor) ki tilawat kar rahe they.
465,"2 log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se nikley, aik Ibaad-bin-Bishr aur doosrey sahib mere khayal ke mutabiq Usaid-bin-Huzair they. raat taareek thi aur donon ashaab ke paas roshan charagh ki tarah koi cheez thi jis se unke aagey-aagey roshni phail rahi thi to jab wo donon ashaab aik doosrey se juda huey to har aik ke sath eik-eik charagh reh gaya jo ghar tak sath raha."
466,"aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutbe mein farmaya ke Allah Taala ne apne aik bandey ko duniya aur aakhirat ke rehney mein ikhtiyar diya (ke wo jis ko chahey ikhtiyar karey) bandey ne wo pasand kya jo Allah ke paas hai yani aakhirat. ye sun kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey, maine apne dil mein kaha ke agar Allah ne apne kisi bandey ko duniya aur aakhirat mein se kisi ko ikhtiyar karne ko kaha aur us bandey ne aakhirat pasand kar li to usmein un buzurg ke roney ki kya wjah hai. lekin ye baat thi ke bandey se murad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi they aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham sabse zyada jaanney waley they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya Abu-Bakar aap roiye mat. apni sohbat aur apni daulat ke zariey tamam logon se zyada mujh par ehsan karne waley aap hi hain aur agar main kisi ko khaleel banata to Abu-Bakar ko banaataa. lekin (jaanii dosti to Allah ke siwa kisi se nahi ho saktii) iske badle mein Islam ki braadrii aur dosti kafi hai. masjid mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf ke darwazey ke siwa tamam darwazey band kar diye jaaein."
467,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne wafat k marz mein bahar tashrif laey. sar pe patti bandhi hui thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par baithey, Allah ki hamd w sana ki aur farmaya, koi shakhs bhi aisa nahi jisne Abu-Bakar bin abu-Qahaafa se zyada mujh par apni jaan w maal ke zariey ehsan kya ho aur agar main kisi ko insanon mein se jaani dost banata to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaataa. lekin Islam ka talluq afzal hai. dekho Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidkii chhod kar us masjid ki tamam khidkiyaan band kar di jaaein."
468,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Makka tashrif laey (aur Makka fateh hua) to aap ne Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulwaya . (jo Kaba ke mutwallii , chaabii bardaar they) unhon-ne darwaza khola to Nabi Karim (sl), Bilaal, Usama-bin-Zaid aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha charon andar tashrif ley gaey. phir darwaza band kar diya gaya aur wahan thodi der tak thahar kar bahar aaey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke maine jaldi se aagey badh kar Bilal se puchha (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba ke andar kya kiya) unhon-ne bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar Namaz padhi thi. maine puchha kis jagah? kaha ke donon sutunon ke darmyaan. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye poochhna mujhey yad na raha ke aap ne kitni rakatein padhi thin."
469,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh sawaaron ko Najad ki taraf bheja tha. wo log banu-Haneefa ke aik shakhs Samaama-bin-Assaal ko (bataur jangi qaidi) pakad laey aur masjid mein aik sutoon se baandh diya.
470,"mein masjide-Nabawi mein khada hua tha, kisi ne meri taraf kankari phenkii . maine jo nazar uthai to dekha ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) samney hain. aap ne farmaya ke ye samney jo 2 log hain unhein mere paas bula kar laao. main bula laya. aap ne puchha ke tumhara talluq kis qabeele se hai ya ye farmaya ke tum kahan rahtey ho? unhon-ne bataya ke ham Taaif ke rehney waley hain. aap ne farmaya ke agar tum Madina ke hotey to main tumhen saza diye baghair na chhorta . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein awaz unchi kartey ho?"
471,"unhon-ne Abdullah ibne- abii-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se apne aik qarz ke silsiley main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein masjide-Nabawi ke andar taqaza kya. donon ki awaz kuchh unchi ho gaee yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi apne hujre se sun liya. aap uthey aur hujre par padey huey parde ko hataya . aap ne Kab-bin-Malik ko awaz di, aey Kab! Kab boley, ya Rasulullah! hazir hun. aap ne apne hath ke ishaarey se bataya ke wo apna aadha qarz maaf kar de. Kab ne kaha ya Rasulullah! maine maaf kar diya. aap ne ibne-abii-Hadrad se farmaya achchha ab chal uth iska qarz ada kar."
472,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ( jabke (us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par they ke raat ki Namaz (yani tahajjud ( kis tarah padhney ke liye aap farmatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke 2-2 rakaat karke padh aur jab subah qareeb honey lagey to aik rakaat padh ley. ye aik rakaat us saari Namaz ko taaq bana degi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke raat ki aakhiri Namaz ko taaq rakha karo kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska hukm diya.
473,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt khutba de rahe they aaney waley ne puchha ke raat ki Namaz kis tarah padhi jaaey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya 2-2 rakaat, phir jabsubah hone ka andesha ho to aik rakaat witr ki padh ley taake tu ney jo Namaz padhi hai usey ye rakaat taaq bana de aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke Waleed-bin-kaseer ne kaha ke mujh se Ubaidullaah-bin-Abdullaah Umri ne bayan kya, Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan kya ke aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko awaz di jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they."
474,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they ke teen aadmi bahar se aaey. 2 to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein haziri ki gharaz se aagey badhey lekin teesra chala gaya. un 2 mein se aik ne darmyan mein khali jagah dekhi aur wahan baith gaya. doosra shakhs peechhey baith gaya aur tesraa to wapas hi ja raha tha. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) waz (nasihat) se farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya main tumhen un teenon ke mutaalliq aik baat na bataaun . aik shakhs to Allah ki taraf badha aur Allah ne usey jagah di (yani pahlaa shakhs) raha doosra to usne ( logon mein ghusney se) sharm ki, Allah ne bhi us se sharm ki, teesrey ne munh pher liya. isliye Allah ne bhi uski taraf se munh pher liya."
475,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chit letey huey dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna aik paon doosrey par rakhey huey they. ibne-Shahab Zohri se marwi (bayan) hai, wo Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat kartey hain ke umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi tarah let'tey they."
476,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaya ke maine jab se hosh sanbhaalaa to apne maan-baap ko musalman hi paya aur ham par koi din aisa nahi guzra jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) subah w Sham din ke donon waqt hamarey ghar tashrif na laey hun. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki samajh mein aik tarkeeb aai to unhon-ne ghar ke samney aik masjid bana li, wo usmein Namaz padhtey aur Quran Majeed ki tilawat kartey. mushrekeen ki auratein aur unke bachchey wahan tajjub se suntey aur khadey ho jatey aur aap ki taraf dekhtey rahtey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) badey roney waley aadmi they. jab Quran Karim padhtey to aansuon par qaabu na rehta, Quraish ke mushrik sardar us soorate-haal se ghabraa gaey."
477,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jamat ke sath Namaz padhney mein ghar ke andar ya bazar (dukan wghaira) mein Namaz padhney se pachchis (25) guna sawab zyada milta hai. kyonke jab koi shakhs tum mein se wuzu karey aur uske aadaab ka lihaaz rakhey phir masjid mein sirf Namaz ki gharaz se aaey to iske har qadam par Allah Taala aik darja uska buland karta hai aur aik gunah us se maaf karta hai. is tarah wo masjid ke andar aaeyga. masjid mein aaney ke baad jab tak Namaz ke intizar mein rahega. usey Namaz hi ki haalat mein shumaar kya jaeyga aur jab tak us jagah betha rahe jahan usne Namaz padhi hai to Farishtey uske liye rehmate-khudawandi ki duaein kartey hain ( اللهم اغفر له , Mina ‏‏‏‏اللهم ارحمه (aey Allaah! usko bakhsh de, aey Allaah! is par raham kar. jab tak ke reeh khaarij karke (wo farishton ko) takleef na de."
478,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungliyon ko aik doosrey mein dakhil kya.
479,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungliyon ko aik doosrey mein dakhil kya.
480,Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah-bin-Amr tumhara kya haal hoga jab tum burey logon mein reh jaogey is tarah (yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hath ki ungliyan doosrey hath mein karke dikhlayein).
481,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aik momin doosrey momin ke liye Imaarat ki tarah hai ke iska aik hissey doosrey hisse ko quwwat pahunchata hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hath ki ungliyon ko doosrey hath ki ungliyon mein dakhil kya.
482,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein do-pahar ke baad ki 2 namazon mein se koi Namaz padhai. (zuhar ya Asr ki) Ibne-Sirin ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska naam to liya tha. lekin main bhool gaya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 rakaat Namaz padha kar salam pher diya. iske baad aik lakdi ki laathii se jo masjid mein rakhi hui thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tek laga kar khadey ho gaey. aisa malum hota tha ke jaisey aap bahut hi khafa hon aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne daain hath ko baain hath par rakha aur unki ungliyon ko aik doosrey mein dakhil kya aur aap ne apne daain rukhsar Mubarak ko baain hath ki hatheli se sahara diya. jo log Namaz padh kar jaldi nikal jaya kartey they wo masjid ke darwazon se paar ho gaey. phir log kehney lagey ke kya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai. haaziriin mein Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. lekin unhein bhi aap se bolney ki himmat na hui. unhein mein aik shakhs they jinke hath lambey they aur unhein zul-yadain kaha jata tha. unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhool gaey ya Namaz kam kar di gaee hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke na main bhoola hun aur na Namaz mein koi kami hui hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se poochha. kya zul-yadain sahi keh rahe hain. haaziriin boley ke ji haan! ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey aur baqi rakatein padhin. phir salam phera phir takbeer kahi aur saho ka sajda kya. mamool (routine) ke mutabiq ya us se bhi lamba sajda. phir sar uthaya aur takbeer kahi. phir takbeer kahi aur doosra sajda kya. mamool (routine) ke mutabiq ya usse bhi lamba phir sar uthaya aur takbeer kahii, logon ne baar-baar Ibne-Sirin se puchha ke kya phir salam phera to wo jawab detey ke mujhey khabar di gaee hai ke Imran-bin-Husain kehtey they ke phir salam pheraa."
483,wo (Madina se Makka tak) rastey mein kai jaghon ko dhoondh kar wahan Namaz padhtey aur kehtey ke unke bap Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi un maqamat par Namaz padha kartey they. aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko un maqamat par Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai aur Musa-bin-Aqba ne kaha ke mujh se Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq bayan kya ke wo un maqamat par Namaz padha kartey they. aur maine Salim se puchha to mujhey khub yad hai ke unhon-ne bhi Naafe ke bayan ke mutabiq hi tamam maqamat ka zikr kya. faqat maqam Sharf Roha ki masjid ke mutaalliq donon ne ikhtilaf kya.
484,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Umra ke irade se tashrif le gaey aur Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par jab Haj ke liye nikley to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zul-Hulaifa mein qiyam farmaya, zul-Hulaifa ki masjid ke qareeb Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik babool ke darakht ke nichey utrey aur jab aap kisi jihad se wapas hotey aur rasta zul-Hulaifa se ho kar guzarta ya Haj ya Umra se waapsii hoti to aap wadie-Atiq ke nichle ilaqe mein utartey, phir jab wadi ke nichle ilaqe se uper chadhtey to wadi ke oopri kinarey ke us mashriqii hisse par padao hota jahan kankariyon aur ret ka kushaada nala hai. (yani Batha mein) yahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ko subah tak aaraam farmatey. ye maqam us masjid ke qareeb nahi hai jo pattharon ki bani hai, aap us teeley par bhi nahi hotey jis par masjid bani hui hai. wahan aik gehra naala tha Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) wahin Namaz padhtey. iske nichle ilaqe mein ret ke teeley they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan Namaz padha kartey they. kankariyon aur ret ke kushaada naale ki taraf se sailaab ne aa kar us jagah ke aasaar w nishanat ko paat diya hai, jahan Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padha kartey they."
485,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us jagah Namaz padhi jahan ab Sharf Roha ki masjid ke qareeb aik chhoti masjid hai, Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us jagah ki nishaandehi kartey they jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi. kehtey they ke yahan tumharey daain taraf jab tum masjid main ( qibla ru ho kar) Namaz padhney ke liye khadey hotey ho. jab tum (Madina se) Makka jao to ye chhoti si masjid rastey ke daain taraf padtii hai. iske aur badi masjid ke darmyan aik patthar ki mar ka fasla hai ya us se kuchh kam zyada ."
486,"us chhoti pahaadii ki taraf Namaz padhtey jo Roha ke aakhir kinarey par hai aur ye pahaadii wahan khatm hoti hai jahan rastey ka kinara hai. us masjid ke qareeb jo iske aur Roha ke aakhiri hissey ke beech mein hai Makka ko jatey huey. ab wahan aik masjid bin gaee hai. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us masjid mein Namaz nahi padhtey they balke usko apne baain taraf muqabil mein chhod detey aur aagey badh kar khud pahaadii arq al-Taiba ki taraf Namaz padhtey they. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Roha se chaltey to Zohar us waqt tak na padhtey jab tak us maqam par na pahunch jatey. jab yahan aa jatey to Zohar padhtey, aur agar Makka se aatey huey subah sadiq se thodi der pahley ya sahar ke aakhir mein wahan se guzartey to subah ki Namaz tak wahin aaraam kartey aur fajr ki Namaz padhtey."
487,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rastey ke daain taraf muqabil mein aik ghaney darakht ke nichey wasee aur narm ilaqa mein qiyam farmatey jo Ruvaisa gaanv ke qareeb hai. phir aap us teela se jo Ruvaisa ke rastey se taqriban 2 meel ke faasley par hai chaltey they. ab us darakht ka uper ka hissa toot gaya hai. aur darmyan mein se dohra ho kar jad par khada hai. uski jad mein ret ke bahut se teeley hain.
488,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qariya araj ke qareeb us naley ke kinarey Namaz padhi jo pahaad ki taraf jatey huey padta hai. us masjid ke paas 2 ya teen qabrein hain, un qabron par uper taley patthar rakhey huey hain, rastey ke daain taraf un badey pattharon ke paas jo rastey mein hain. unke darmyan mein ho kar Namaz padhi, Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) qariya araj se suraj dhalney ke baad chaltey aur Zohar usi masjid mein aa kar padha kartey they."
489,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rastey ke baain taraf un ghaney darakhton ke paas qiyam farmaya jo harshii pahaad ke nazdeek nichle ilaqe mein hain. ye dhalwan jagah harshii ke aik kinarey se mili hui hai. yahan se aam raaste tak pahunchne ke liye teer ki mar ka fasla hai. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) us badey darakht ki taraf Namaz padhtey they jawan tamam darakhton mein rastey se sabse zyada nazdeek hai aur sabse lamba darakht bhi yahi hai.
490,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us naley mein utra kartey they jo wadi marruz-zohraan ke nasheb mein hai. Madina ke muqabil jabke maqam Safravat se utra jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us dhalwan ke bilkul nasheb mein qiyam kartey they. ye rastey ke baain taraf padta hai jab koi shakhs Makka ja raha ho (jisko ab batan maro kehtey hain) rastey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki manzil ke darmyan sirf aik patthar hi ke mar ka fasla hota.
491,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam zi tuwa mein qiyam farmatey aur raat yahin guzara kartey they aur subah hoti to namaze-Fajr yahin padhtey . Makka jatey huey. yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Namaz padhney ki jagah aik badey se teeley par thi. us masjid mein nahi jo ab wahan bani hui hai balke us se nichey aik bada teelaa tha.
492,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us pahaad ke donon konon ka rukh kya jo iske aur Jabale-Taweel ke darmyan Kaba ki samt hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us masjid ko jo ab wahan tameer hui hai apni baain taraf kar letey teeley ke kinarey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Namaz padhney ki jagah us se nichey siyah teeley par thi teeley se taqriban das hath chhod kar pahaad ki donon ghatiyon ki taraf rukh karke Namaz padhtey jo tumharey aur Kaba ke darmyan hai.
493,mein aik gadhi par Sawar ho kar aaya. us zamane mein baligh honey wala tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Mina mein logon ko Namaz padha rahe they. lekin diwar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney na thi. main saf ke kuchh hissey se guzar kar sawari se utra aur maine gadhi ko charney ke liye chhod diya aur saf mein dakhil ho gaya. to kisi ne mujh par aetraz nahi kya.
494,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab eid ke din (Madina se) bahar tashrif ley jatey to chhotey neze (barchhii) ko gaadney ka hukm detey wo jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey gaad diya jata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski taraf rukh karke Namaz padhtey aur log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey khadey hotey. yahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein bhi kya kartey they. (musalmanon ke) khulafaa ne usi wjah se barchha sath rakhney ki aadat bana li hai.
495,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko Batha mein Namaz padhai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney anza (danda jiske nichey phal laga hua ho) gaad diya gaya tha. (chunkey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) musafir they is liye) Zohar ki 2 rakaat aur Asr ki 2 rakaat ada kin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney se auratein aur gadhey guzar rahe they.
496,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sajda karne ki jagah aur diwar ke darmyan aik bakri ke guzar sakney ka fasla rehta tha.
497,masjid ki diwar aur member ke darmyan bakri ke guzar sakney ke faasley ke barabar jagah thi.
498,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye barchha gaad diya jata Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski taraf Namaz padhtey they.
499,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) do-pahar ke waqt bahar tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein wuzu ka pani pesh kya gaya, jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya. phir hamein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhai aur Asr ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney anza gaad diya gaya tha aur auratein aur gadhey par Sawar log iske peechhey se guzar rahe they."
500,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab rafa haajat (peshab-pakhaney se farigh honey) ke liye nikaltey to main aur aik aur ladka Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey peechhey jatey. hamarey sath Ukaza (danda jiske nichey lohey ka phal laga hua ho) ya chhadi ya anza hota aur hamarey sath aik chhaagal bhi hota tha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haajat se farigh ho jatey to ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wo chhaagal de detey they.
501,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas do-pahar ke waqt tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Batha mein Zohar aur Asr ki 2-2 rakatein padhin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney neza gaad diya gaya tha aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya to log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ke pani ko apne badan par laga rahe they.
502,main Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath (masjide-Nabawi mein) hazir hua karta tha. Salma (Raziallahu anhu) hamesha us sutoon ko samney karke Namaz padhtey jahan Quran sharif rakha rehta tha. maine unse kaha ke aey abu-Muslim ! main dekhta hun ke aap hamesha usi sutoon ko samney karke Namaz padhtey hain. unhon-ne farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khas taur se usi sutoon ko samney karke Namaz padha kartey they.
503,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke badey badey sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo maghrib (ki azan (ke waqt sutunon ki taraf lapaktey aur Shoba ne Amr bin Aamir se unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se (is hadis mein) ye zyadti ki hai. ''yahan tak ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hujrey se bahar tashrif laatey.''
504,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah ke andar tashrif le gaey aur Usaama-bin-Zaid Usman-bin-Talha aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) der tak andar rahe. phir bahar aaey aur main sab logon se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey hi wahan aaya. maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kahan Namaz padhi thi. unhon-ne bataya ke aagey ke 2 sutunon ke beech mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi.
505,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke andar tashrif le gaey aur Usaama-bin-Zaid, Bilal aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha Hajabi bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kaba ka darwaza band kar diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein thahrey rahe. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar nikley to maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne andar kya kiya? unhon-ne kaha ke aap ne aik sutoon ko to baain taraf chhoda aur aik ko daain taraf aur teen ko peechhey aur us zamane mein khaana Kaba mein 6 sutoon they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke ham se Ismail-bin-Abi-Idrees ne kaha, wo kehtey hain ke mujh se Imam Malik ne ye hadis yun bayan ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne daain taraf 2 sutoon chhodey they."
506,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) jab Kaba mein dakhil hotey to seedhey munh ke samney chaley jatey. darwaza peeth ki taraf hota aur aap aagey badhtey jab unke aur samney ki diwar ka fasla qareeb teen hath ke reh jata to Namaz padhtey. is tarah aap us jagah Namaz padhna chahtey they jiske mutaalliq Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko bataya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahin Namaz padhi thi. aap farmatey they ke Baitullah mein jis koney mein ham chaahein Namaz padh saktey hain. usmein koi qabahat nahi hai.
507,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari ko samney chaudai mein kar letey aur uski taraf munh karke Namaz padhtey they, Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se puchha ke jab sawari uchhalney koodney lagti to us waqt aap kya kiya kartey they? Naafe ne kaha ke aap us waqt kajaawey ko apne samney kar letey aur uske aakhiri hissey ki (jis par Sawar tek lagata hai aik khadi si lakdi ki) taraf munh karke Namaz padhtey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi isi tarah kya kartey they."
508,"aap ne farmaya tum logon ne ham aurton ko kutton aur gadhon ke barabar bana diya. halanke main charpai par leti rehti thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur charpai ke beech mein aa jatey (ya charpai ko apne aur qibley ke beech mein kar letey) phir Namaz padhtey. mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney padaa rehna bura malum hota, isliye main paaintii ki taraf se khisak ke lihaf se bahar nikal jati."
509,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (doosri sanad) aur ham se Aadam-bin-abii-Ayaas ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne, kaha ham se Humaid bin Hilal Adwi ne, kaha ham se Abu-Saleh Samaan ne, kaha maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko Juma ke din Namaz padhtey huey dekha. aap kisi cheez ki taraf munh kiye huey logon ke liye usey aad banaey huey they. Abu-Mueet ke beton mein se aik jawan ne chaha ke aap ke samney se ho kar guzar jaey. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske seene par dhakka de kar roke rakhna chaha . jawan ne charon taraf nazar daudaatii lekin koi rasta siwaey samney se guzarney ke na mila. isliye wo phir usi taraf se nikalney ke liye lota . ab abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahley se bhi zyada zor se dhakka diya. usey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se shikayat hui aur wo apni ye shikayat Marwan ke paas ley gaya. iske baad abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bhi tashrif ley gaey. Marwan ne kaha aey abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aap main aur aap ke bhatijey mein kya mamla pesh aaya. aap ne farmaya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jab koi shakhs Namaz kisi cheez ki taraf munh karke padhey aur us cheez ko aad bana raha ho phir bhi agar koi samney se guzrey to usey rok dena chahiye agar ab bhi usey israar ho to usey ladna chahiye kyonke wo shaitan hai."
510,Zaid-bin-Khalid ne unhein abu-Jaheem Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein unse ye baat poochhney ke liye bheja ke unhon-ne Namaz padhney waley ke samney se guzarney waley ke mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya suna hai. abu-Jaheem ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar namazi ke samney se guzarney wala janta ke iska kitna bada gunah hai to iske samney se guzarney par chalis (40) tak wahin khadey rehney ko tarjeeh deta. abu-Nazar ne kaha ke mujhey yad nahi ke Basar-bin-Saeed ne chalis (40) din kaha ya mahina ya saal.
511,"unke samney zikr hua ke Namaz ko kya cheezein tod deti hain, logon ne kaha ke kutta , gadhaa aur aurat ( bhi) Namaz ko tod deti hai. (jab samney aa jaey) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke tum ne hamein kutton ke barabar bana diya. halanke main janti hon ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh rahe they. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qible ke darmyan ( samney ( charpai par leti hui thi. mujhey zarurat pesh aati thi aur ye bhi achchha nahi malum hota tha ke khud ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kar dun. isliye main aahista se nikal aati thi. Aamash ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Aaisha se isi tarah ye hadis bayan ki."
512,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey rahtey aur main (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saamney) bichhoney par aadi soti hui padi hoti. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) witr padhna chahtey to mujhey bhi jaga detey aur main bhi witr padh leti thi.
513,"aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney so jaya karti thi. mere paon Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney ( phailey huey) hotey . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey to paon ko halkey se daba detey aur main unhein suked leti phir jab qiyam farmatey to main unhein phaila leti thi us zamane mein gharon ke andar charagh nahi hotey they. ( malum hua ke aisa karna bhi jaaiz hai)."
514,"unke samney un chizon ka zikr hua. jo Namaz ko tod deti hain yani kutta , gadhaa aur aurat . is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke tum logon ne hamein gadhon aur kutton ke barabar kar diya. halanke khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is tarah Namaz padhtey they ke main charpai par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur qible ke beech mein leti rehti thi. mujhey koi zarurat pesh aai aur chunkey ye baat pasand na thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (jab ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh rahe hon ( baithoon aur is tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef ho. isliye main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paon ki taraf se khamoshi ke sath nikal jati thi."
515,"kya Namaz ko koi cheez tod deti hai? to unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi, usey koi cheez nahi todti. kyonke mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar raat ko Namaz padhtey aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aur qible ke darmyan arz mein bistar par leti rehti thi."
516,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umaama-bint-Zainab-binte-Rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (kabhi-kabhi) Namaz padhtey waqt uthaey hotey they. abul-Aas-bin-Rabee-bin-Abd-Shams ki hadis mein hai ke sajde mein jatey to utaar detey aur jab qiyam farmatey to utha letey.
517,mera bistar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke musalley ke barabar mein hota tha aur kuchh baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kapda (namaz padhtey mein) mere uper aa jata aur main apne bistar par hi hoti thi.
518,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey hotey aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barabar mein soti rehti . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein jatey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka kapda mujhey chhu jata halanke main haaiza hoti thi.
519,tum ne bura kya ke ham ko kutton aur gadhon ke hukm mein kar diya. khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh rahe they. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney leti hui thi. jab sajda karna chahtey to mere paon ko chhu detey aur main unhein suked leti thi.
520,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke paas khadey Namaz padh rahe they. Quraish apni majlis main ( qareeb hi ( baithey huey they. itney mein unmein se aik qureshi bola us dikhawa karne waaley ko nahi dekhtey ? kya koi hai jo falan qabeele ke zabah kiye huey oont ka gobar, khoon aur ojhdii utha laey. phir yahan intizar kare. jab ye (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) sajde mein jaey to gardan par rakh de (chunanche us kaam ko anjam dene ke liye) unmein se sabse zyada bad-bakht shakhs utha aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde mein gaey to usne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan Mubarak par ye ghilazatein daal din. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajde hi ki haalat mein sar rakhey rahe. mushrekeen (ye dekh kar) hansey aur maarey hansi ke aik doosrey par lot-pot hone lagey. aik shakhs (ghaaliban ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey. wo abhi bachcha thin. aap (Raziallahu anhu) daudti hui aaein . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ab bhi sajde hi mein they. phir (Faatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne) un ghilazaton ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper se hataya aur mushrekeen ko bura-bhala kaha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz poori karke farmaya'' ya Allah Quraish par azab nazil kar. ya Allah Quraish par azab nazil kar. ya Allah Quraish par azab nazil kar.'' phir naam lekar kaha ya Allah ! Amr bin Hisham , Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba bin Rabee , Waleed bin Utba , Umayya-bin-Khalaf , Aqba bin abi mueet aur Umara ibne- Waleed ko halaak kar. Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Allah ki qism ! maine un sab ko badr ki ladai mein maqtool paya. phir unhein ghaseet kar badr ke kuwein mein phenk diya gaya. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuwein waley Allah ki rehmat se door kar diye gaey."
